Yetunde Ayeni-Babaeko (a mụrụ n'afọ 1978) bụ onye Naijiria na-ese foto.
A mụrụ Yetunde Ayeni-Babaeko na Enugu, Mpaghara Ọwụwa Anyanwụ, Naijiria n'afọ 1978
Nna ya bụ onye Naijiria na nne ya bụ onye Germany
Ọ kwagara Germany mgbe ọ bụ nwata, na-aga ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị n'ebe ahụ ma gụchaa akwụkwọ foto na Studio Be na Greven
N'afọ 2007, o mepere ụlọ ọrụ nke ya, Camera Studios, nke dị na Ikeja.

Ihe ngosi Ayeni-Babaeko nke afọ 2014 'Eko Moves', na mmekorita ya na Society for Performing Arts of Nigeria (SPAN), gosipụtara ndị na-agba egwu n'ebe ọha na eze na Lagos. Ihe ngosi ya nke afọ 2019 'White Ebony' gosipụtara ọnọdụ nke ndị nwere albinism.
